gs-pltr-alex-karp-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20surged%20as%20much%20as%2028%25%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20announced%20strong%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20results%20and%20offered%20upbeat%202025%20guidance%20that%20beat%20analyst%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20analytics%20company%2C%20which%20uses%20AI%20technologies%20to%20service%20customers%20including%20the%20US%20government%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20stock%20soar%2035%25%20year-to-date%2C%20after%20a%20341%25%20gain%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20stock%20that's%20been%20on%20such%20a%20hot%20streak%2C%20Palantir%20has%20relatively%20few%20bullish%20calls%20from%20analysts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bloomberg%20data%2C%20Palantir%20stock%20has%20just%20four%20buy%20ratings%2C%2015%20holds%2C%20and%20five%20sells.%20Other%20software%20firms%20doing%20business%20in%20AI%20and%20with%20similar%20valuations%20to%20Palantir's%20have%20more%20bulls%20in%20their%20corner.%20Snowflake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%2036%20buy%20ratings%2C%2010%20holds%2C%20and%20two%20sells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fpalantir-stock-price-ai-q4-earnings-pltr-alex-karp-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblockbuster%20earnings%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20the%20bears%20don't%20seem%20convinced.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBard%20Zelnick%2C%20research%20analyst%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20admitted%20in%20a%20Monday%20note%20that%20Palantir's%20earnings%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impressive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20report%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20change%20his%20%26quot%3BSell%26quot%3B%20rating%20on%20the%20stock.%20Zelnick%20is%20ultimately%20worried%20about%20Palantir's%20high%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20our%20issue%20with%20the%20stock%20really%20boils%20down%20to%20valuation%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelnick%20said.%20%26quot%3BPLTR's%20shares%20are%20trading%20at%20~50x%20an%20upside%20CY26%20revenue%2C%20which%20history%20suggests%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20grow%20into%2C%20especially%20at%20this%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20Palantir's%20premium%20valuation%20into%20perspective%2C%20Zelnick%20said%20the%20stock%20trades%20at%20over%20triple%20the%20revenue%20multiple%20of%20the%20next%20most%20expensive%20stock%20that%20he%20covers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelnick%20increased%20his%20price%20target%20to%20%2450%20from%20%2435%2C%20representing%20potential%20downside%20of%2051%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20Jefferies%2C%20led%20by%20Brent%20Thill%2C%20are%20similarly%20unconvinced.%20The%20analysts%20commended%20the%20tech%20firm's%20earnings%20results%20and%20said%20that%20fundamentals%20have%20been%20strong%20and%20will%20likely%20accelerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20for%20Palantir%20to%20sustain%20its%20current%20stock%20price%2C%20its%20underlying%20business%20would%20have%20to%20grow%20at%20an%20incredible%20rate%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCY25%20rev%20guide%20implies%2031%25%20growth%20vs%2029%25%20in%20CY24%2C%20and%20PLTR%20would%20need%20to%20accel%20growth%20to%2050%25%20for%204%20years%20and%20trade%20at%2018x%20CY28E%20rev%20just%20to%20hold%20its%20stock%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Thill%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20still%20leave%20Palantir%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20stocks%20in%20software%20even%20four%20years%20out%2C%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies%20also%20questioned%20Palantir's%20sales%20tactics%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20limited%20sales%20force%26quot%3B%20despite%20the%20company's%20strong%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20commend%20product%20led-growth%20but%20question%20the%20reluctance%20to%20invest%20more%20in%20an%20enterprise%20sales%20mo