%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20like%20Meta%20and%20Amazon%20have%20been%20scaling%20back%20their%20DEI%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEuropean%20tech%20industry%20insiders%20say%20the%20continent%20may%20follow%20the%20US'%20lead.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20could%20result%20in%20Europe's%20tech%20firms%20refining%20DEI%20policies%2C%20said%20Hannah%20Leach%2C%20partner%20at%20Antler.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20is%20rolling%20back%20DEI%20measures.%20Europe's%20tech%20sector%20is%20yet%20to%20feel%20the%20same%20pressure%2C%20but%20industry%20insiders%20expect%20some%20of%20the%20sentiment%20from%20the%20US%20to%20spill%20over%20across%20the%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20and%20Amazon%20have%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-rolls-back-dei-programs-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escaled%20back%20their%20diversity%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20a%20wider%20pushback%20against%20DEI%20in%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20and%20investors%20in%20Europe%20see%20it%20as%20an%20omen%20of%20what%20could%20transpire%20on%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20can%20be%20a%20lead%20indicator%20of%20what%20could%20happen%20in%20Europe%20concerning%20diversity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodney%20Appiah%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Cornerstone%20VC%2C%20a%20fund%20that%20backs%20underrepresented%20founders.%20%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20we%20are%20probably%20four%20to%20five%20years%20away%20from%20that%20sort%20of%20translating%20into%20Europe%20and%20certainly%20into%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAppiah%20pointed%20to%20the%20collaborative%20nature%20of%20the%20tech%20and%20VC%20industry%20and%20the%20UK's%20dependency%20on%20the%20US%20tech%20market.%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20narrative%20will%20eventually%20have%20a%20contributing%20factor%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20Europe%20moves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22629c2887-88c9-41bb-ad19-5211d65858a0%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20inspiration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDiversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20programs%20in%20Europe%20could%20come%20under%20pressure%20if%20big-name%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20continue%20to%20scale%20back%20initiatives%2C%20said%20Michael%20Smets%2C%20professor%20at%20Oxford's%20Said%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20companies%20have%20global%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20Smets%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20Microsoft%20et%20al.%20would%20roll%20back%20DEI%20programs%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20not%20in%20Europe%2C%20seems%20na%C3%AFve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Microsoft%20has%20not%20announced%20any%20recent%20rollbacks%20of%20DEI%20initiatives%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-dei-leader-email-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20a%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20tech%20companies%20would%20also%20look%20to%20their%20larger%20peers%20in%20the%20US%20for%20%26quot%3Binspiration%2C%26quot%3B%20Smets%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20leaders%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20navigate%20an%20uncertain%2C%20new%20situation%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20copy%20leading%20organizations%20in%20their%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BDoing%20the%20same%20as%20Big%20Tech%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20right%20or%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20is%20much%20more%20defensible%20than%20the%20bold%20choice%20of%20going%20against%20the%20grain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20US%20corporate%20heavyweights%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-doubles-down-jpmorgan-diversity-efforts-dei-shareholder-activists-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20as%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20said%20they%20remain%20committed%20to%20DEI%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a216d5b6-4a79-4788-90cf-c6118a0c792f%5C%22%3EDEI%20differences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEurope's%20tech%20companies%20may%20look%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20for%20inspiration%2C%20but%20they%20have%20historically%20had%20different%20approaches%20to%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20founders%20and%20investors%20often%20cite%20the%20benefits%20DEI%20efforts%20can%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20return%20on%20investment%20on%20DEI%20has%20been%20forgotten%20about%20as%20everything%20has%20become%20politicized%2C%26quot%3B%20Amardeep%20Parmar%2C%20cofounder%20of%20BAE%20HQ%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20British-Asian%20entrepreneurs%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20hiring%20from%20underrepresented%20groups%20gives%20companies%20access%20to%20a%20wider%20talent%20pool.%20That%20can%20lead%20to%20commercial%20benefits%2C%20Parmar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20aren't%20so%20easy%20to%20fool%2C%20though%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20to%20match%20your%20words%20with%20your%20actions%20%E2%80%94%20we%20returned%203-8x%20for%20our%20sponsor%20organizations%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20issued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20orders%20to%20scrap%20DEI%20offices%20and%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20revoked%20a%20civil%20rights-era%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-equal-employment-opportunity-act-explained-dei-businesses-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEqual%20Employment%20Opportunity%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Trump%2C%20along%20with%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20instead%20called%20for%20an%20approach%20that%20prioritizes%20meritocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadha%20Vyas%2C%20cof