%20Wall%20Street%20titans%2C%20like%20JPMorgan%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20have%20enforced%20strict%20RTO%20mandates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20pandemic%20restrictions%20lifted%2C%20Wall%20Street's%20biggest%20names%20have%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20to%20get%20employees%20back%20to%20their%20desks.%20But%20Citigroup%20is%20standing%20firm%20behind%20its%20hybrid%20work%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20will%20continue%20to%20allow%20most%20employees%20to%20work%20from%20home%20two%20days%20a%20week%2C%20the%20US%20bank's%20chief%20executive%20Jane%20Fraser%20told%20executives%20during%20a%20quarterly%20call%20in%20mid-January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F12b94232-8d89-4f81-8ac8-df97c9c90106%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Citi%20employees%20are%20required%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%20and%20can%20work%20remotely%20for%20two%20days.%20Bank%20branch%20employees%20and%20most%20traders%20are%20required%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20call%2C%20Fraser%20reportedly%20said%20that%20offering%20hybrid%20work%20gives%20Citi%20an%20advantage%20over%20its%20competitors%20and%20could%20be%20a%20recruitment%20tool%20to%20draw%20in%20employees%2C%20the%20FT%20first%20reported%20and%20Business%20Insider%20has%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFraser%20has%20previously%20characterized%20working%20from%20home%20as%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right.%20At%20the%202023%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20she%20said%20the%20bank%20was%20calling%20workers%20with%20productivity%20issues%20back%20to%20their%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Fraser%20doubles%20down%20on%20hybrid%20work%20at%20Citi%2C%20the%20bank%20is%20spending%20big%20on%20new%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti%20is%20spending%20%C2%A31%20billion%20(%241.2%20billion)%20to%20renovate%20its%20London%20office%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bworkplace%20for%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%20The%20Citi%20Tower%20in%20Canary%20Wharf%20is%20due%20to%20open%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti's%20approach%20is%20less%20strict%20than%20most%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-rto-banks-hedge-funds-private-equity-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20competitors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20banks%20to%20re-introduce%20five%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office.%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20called%20remote%20work%20an%20%26quot%3Baberration%26quot%3B%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20JPMorgan%20had%20roughly%2050%25%20of%20employees%20back%20in%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20This%20January%2C%20it%20announced%20that%20it%20was%20ending%20hybrid%20work%20and%20bringing%20all%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20starting%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20some%20of%20you%20prefer%20a%20hybrid%20schedule%20and%20respectfully%20understand%20that%20not%20everyone%20will%20agree%20with%20this%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-return-to-office-memo-ending-remote-work-jamie-dimon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20it%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20run%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20spokesman%20said%20that%20roughly%2070%25%20of%20the%20bank's%20employees%20were%20already%20back%20in%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20RTO%20push%20comes%20as%20JPMorgan%20prepares%20to%20open%20a%20newly%20refurbished%20global%20headquarters%20at%20270%20Park%20Avenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20With%20space%20to%20house%20up%20to%2014%2C000%20employees%2C%20the%20building%20will%20set%20%26quot%3Bnew%2