%20granted%20permanent%20residency%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20deported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%207%2C25%2C000%20illegal%20immigrants%20from%20India%20live%20in%20the%20US%2C%20making%20it%20the%20third-largest%20population%20of%20unauthorised%20immigrants%20after%20Mexico%20and%20El%20Salvador%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20from%20Punjab%2C%20who%20are%20now%20facing%20deportation%2C%20had%20entered%20the%20US%20through%20the%20%26quot%3Bdonkey%20route%26quot%3B%20or%20other%20illegal%20means%20by%20spending%20lakhs%20of%20rupees.%20The%20US%20administration%20has%20launched%20a%20crackdown%20against%20illegal%20immigrants%20after%20Trump%20became%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738748220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ft68u1bh8_-us-military-c17-aircraft-afp_625x300_05_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fillegal-indian-immigrants-from-us-land-in-punjab-48-below-age-of-25-in-first-batch-of-illegal-indian-immigrants-from-us-7639688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20military%20aircraft%20carrying%20first%20batch%20of%20104%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%2030%20each%20were%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20reached%20Amritsar%20in%20Punjab%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fillegal-indian-immigrants-from-us-land-in-punjab-48-below-age-of-25-in-first-batch-of-illegal-indian-immigrants-from-us-7639688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2218-Year-Old%20Migrant%20Sexually%20Assaulted%20In%20Moving%20Auto-Rickshaw%20Near%20Chenna