ls%20has%20taken%20amid%20reports%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20flying%20to%20the%20US%20next%20week.%20This%20will%20be%20his%20first%20visit%20after%20Trump%20took%20over%20as%20US%20President%20for%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20has%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20assured%20him%20that%20India%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20back%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants.%20According%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20News%20report%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20have%20identified%2018%2C000-odd%20Indian%20migrants%20who%20entered%20the%20US%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20New%20Delhi%20is%20open%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%20return%26quot%3B%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20living%20'illegally'%20abroad%2C%20including%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%2C%20we%20are%20locating%20and%20loading%20illegal%20aliens%20into%20military%20aircraft%20and%20flying%20them%20back%20to%20the%20places%20from%20which%20they%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20said%20India%20is%20against%20illegal%20immigration%20because%20it%20is%20linked%20to%20several%20forms%20of%20organised%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Indians%20not%20just%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20if%20they%20are%20Indian%20nationals%20and%20they%20are%20overstaying%2C%20or%20they%20are%20in%20a%20particular%20country%20without%20proper%20documentation%2C%20we%20will%20take%20them%20back%2C%20provided%20documents%20are%20shared%20with%20us%20so%20that%20we%20can%20verify%20their%20nationality%20and%20that%20they%20are%20indeed%20Indians.%20If%20that%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20we%20will%20take%20things%20forward%20and%20facilitate%20their%