nox%20theatres.%20Other%20romantic%20movies%20like%20'Chandni'%2C%20'Kabhi%20Kabhie'%2C%20'Aaradhana'%2C%20and%20'Aawara'%20are%20also%20set%20for%20re-release%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famitabh-bachchan-jaya-bachchan-rekhas-silsila-sridevis-chandni-to-re-release-in-theatres-on-valentines-week-details-inside%2Farticleshow%2F117943878.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Deva%3A%20Why%20Bollywood%20Loves%20Bachchan%2C%20But%20Not%20His%20Rebellion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0was%20all%20about%20its%20climax.%20Roshan%20Andrrews'%20seminal%202013%20thriller%20moved%20towards%20a%20finale%20so%20audacious%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20future.%20A%20twist%20not%20just%20ahead%20of%20its%20time%2C%20but%20one%20that%20cemented%20Malayalam%20cinema's%20conceit%3A%20to%20tell%20stories%20that%20don't%20just%20unfold%20but%20upend%2C%20where%20character%20is%20inseparable%20from%20conscience%2C%20and%20narrative%20from%20the%20world%20it%20dares%20to%20reflect.%20A%20conclusion%20that%20not%20only%20sealed%20the%20film's%20denotative%20arc%20but%20opened%20endless%20connotative%20readings.%20A%20revelation%20that%20Antony%20(Prithviraj)%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20wrestling%20with%20the%20weight%20of%20his%20hidden%20sexuality%2C%20takes%20the%20most%20dramatic%20step%20by%20killing%20his%20own%20colleague%20to%20shield%20a%20secret%20the%20world%20had%20already%20taught%20him%20to%20dread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E%20Was%20Depth%20Over%20Highlights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20those%20thrillers%20where%20twists%20exist%20simply%20to%20shock%2C%20this%20one%20existed%20to%20disarm.%20And%20unlike%20those%20thrillers%20in%20which%20revelations%20feel%20abrupt%2C%20imposed%2C%20or%20sensational%2C%20this%20one%20was%20always%20inevitable%3B%20if%20only%20we%20had%20been%20watching%20closely%2C%20with%20the%20right%20gaze.%20It%20revealed%20Antony%20as%20a%20tragic%20figure%2C%20his%20aggression%20a%20smokescreen%2C%20his%20violence%20a%20performance%E2%80%94a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20conform%20to%20the%20rigid%20architecture%20of%20masculinity.%20The%20weight%20of%20scrutiny%20forces%20him%20into%20an%20existence%20dictated%20by%20fear.%20So%2C%20like%20any%20great%20thriller%2C%20its%20denouement%20was%20shaped%20by%20a%20resolution%20that%20was%20not%20just%20a%20conclusion%20but%20a%20consequence.%20Like%20any%20great%20thriller%2C%20it%20was%20crafted%20with%20both%20flair%20and%20spine.%20And%2C%20like%20any%20great%20thriller%2C%20it%20left%20us%20with%20a%20surplus%20of%20technique%20over%20gimmickry%2C%20of%20subtextual%20depth%20over%20textual%20highlights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20chooses%20to%20adapt%20it%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20remake%20it%2C%20it%20should%20be%20obvious%20that%20the%20climax%20is%20untouchable.%20The%20setting%20can%20shift%2C%20the%20narrative%20can%20bend%2C%20characters%20can%20be%20reshaped%2C%20but%20that%20final%20revelation%20must%20remain%20unchanged.%20It%20isn't%20meant%20to%20be%20reimagined%2C%20but%20only%20replicated%2C%20with%20fidelity.%20Its%20essence%20preserved%2C%20its%20weight%20undisturbed.%20No%20wonder%2C%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20written%20in%20reverse%2C%20every%20plot%20point%20taken%20from%20the%20inevitability%20of%20its%20climax%E2%80%94much%20like%20Christopher%20Nolan's%20%3Cem%3EMemento%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2000).%20It's%20a%20screenwriting%20feat%20so%20meticulously%20crafted%20that%20the%20only%20real%20task%20is%20to%20honour%20what's%20already%20on%20the%20page.%20After%20all%2C%20even%20in%20a%20world%20that%20manufactures%20homophobia%20afresh%20each%20day%2C%20this%20twist%20remains%20urgent.%20It%20was%20relevant%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20and%20will%20be%20just%20as%20hauntingly%20relevant%20a%20decade%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDeva%20%3C%2Fem%3EIs%20A%20Predictable%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeva%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20newly%20released%20Hindi%20remake%20of%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20also%20all%20about%20its%20climax.%20Starring%20Shahid%20Kapoor%2C%20it%20moves%20towards%20a%20finale%20that%20has%20become%20a%20talking%20point%E2%80%94but%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20Where%20the%20original%20delivered%20a%20seminal%20twist%2C%20this%20one%20settles%20for%20something%20timid.%20A%20revelation%20so%20simplistic%20that%20even%20in%20isolation%2C%20it%20feels%20unconvincing.%20A%20conclusion%20that%20doesn't%20just%20alter%20the%20original's%20impact%20but%20erases%20it%20entirely%2C%20reducing%20the%20climax%20to%20a%20predictable%20battle%20between%20right%20and%20wrong.%20Dev%20(Shahid%20Kapoor)%20is%20ultimately%20revealed%20to%20be%20not%20a%20man%20tormented%20by%20identity%20but%20simply%20a%20corrupt%20officer%2C%20complicit%20in%20the%20system%20for%20personal%20gain.%20He%20kills%20his%20colleague%20not%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20but%20to%20conceal%20his%20own%20incompetence%20from%20public%20disgrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20becomes%20fascinating%2C%20then%2C%20to%20place%20both%20films%20side%20by%20side%2C%20their%20climaxes%20in%20juxtaposition%3A%20not%20to%20weigh%20one%20against%20the%20other%2C%20nor%20merely%20to%20trace%20their%20narrative%20divergences%2C%20but%20to%20look%20deeper.%C2%A0Both%20offer%20revealing%20insights%2C%20not%20just%20into%20the%20cinematic%20traditions%20of%20their%20respective%20industries%2C%20but%20how%20spectatorship%20shifts%20across%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Ailing%20Bollywood%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Cem%3EDeva%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20reflection%20is%20damning.%20It%20embodies%20everything%20amiss%20in%20contemporary%20Bollywood%3A%20its%20reluctance%2C%20its%20complacency%2C%20its%20instinct%20to%20retreat%20from%20risk.%20It's%20now%20an%20industry%20quick%20to%20remake%2C%20whether%20from%20the%20South%20or%20beyond%2C%20but%20hesitant%20to%20unsettle.%20It%20strips%20away%20complexity%2C%20smooths%20out%20rough%20edges%2C%20sands%20down%20every%20sharp%20truth%2C%20until%20all%20that%20remains%20is%20something%20safe%2C%20palatable.%20Nuance%20is%20sacrificed%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20mass%20appeal.%20The%20result%3F%20Films%20that%20seek%20to%20please%20the%20crowd%20yet%20fear%20provoking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dev%2C%20violence%20isn't%20a%20shield%3B%20it's%20indulgence.%20Where%20Antony%20wielded%20it%20to%20survive%2C%20Dev%20brandishes%20it%20to%20thrive.%20One%20kills%20to%20conceal%2C%20the%20other%20to%20conquer.%20Antony's%20crime%20was%20born%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20%C2%A0an%20instinct%20to%20escape%20the%20noose%20of%20a%20world%20that%20would%20rather%20erase%20him%20than%20accept%20him.%20Dev's%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20is%20rooted%20in%20ambition%2C%20his%20brutality%20a%20currency%20in%20a%20system%20that%20rewards%20dominance.%20He%20wears%20masculinity%20like%20armour%2C%20always%20taking%20pride%20in%20it.%20Antony%20was%20different.%20The%20alpha%20image%20was%20not%20his%20aspiration%2C%20but%20his%20prison.%20It%20was%20a%20mask%20he%20never%20chose%20yet%20was%20forced%20to%20wear.%20Unlike%20Dev%2C%20he%20does%20not%20revel%20in%20it%3B%20simply%20suffocates%20beneath%20it.%20It%20spoke%20volumes%20of%20the%20acceptance%20woven%20into%20the%20fabric%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%2C%20of%20an%20audience%20that%20embraces%20stories%20with%20a%20spine%2C%20of%20an%20industry%20unafraid%20to%20provoke%2C%20to%20challenge%2C%20to%20hold%20a%20mirror%20to%20the%20world.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20leaps%20taken%20by%20its%20frontrunners%2C%20to%20actors%20like%20Prithviraj%20who%20dared%20to%20embody%20a%20gay%20police%20officer%2C%20confronting%20the%20heteronormative%20masculinity%20that%20the%20genre%20so%20often%20glorifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Reflection%20Of%20Choices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Andrrews%20(who%20has%20also%20directed%20%3Cem%3EDeva%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20having%20already%20crafted%20that%20audacious%20climax%20once%2C%20chose%20to%20deviate%20in%20another%20direction%E2%80%94not%20out%20of%20hesitation%2C%20but%20intent.%20Perhaps%20he%20wished%20to%20defy%20expectation%2C%20to%20dismantle%20the%20certainty%20of%20a%20known%20ending%2C%20and%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20shock.%20If%20seen%20through%20this%20lens%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20just%20a%20lesser%20imitation%20but%20a%20distinct%20departure.%20A%20film%20that%2C%20for%20all%20its%20failings%2C%20offers%20some%20insight%20into%20how%20stories%20mutate%20when%20told%20differently%2C%20how%20a%20filmmaker%20grapples%20with%20his%20own%20past%2C%20and%20how%20a%20shift%20in%20vision%20can%20reveal%20not%20just%20what%20was%20changed%2C%20but%20why.%20Perhaps%20then%2C%20it%20holds%20something%20worth%20examining%E2%80%94not%20as%20a%20remake%2C%20but%20as%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20choices%20that%20shape%20adaptation%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20the%20way%20%3Cem%3EDeva%20%3C%2Fem%3Eopens%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20latter%20opens%20over%20a%20Sudoku%20grid%2C%20solving%20itself%2C%20numbers%20shifting%2C%20logic%20falling%20into%20place%2C%20immediately%20marking%20its%20identity%20as%20a%20murder%20mystery.%20%3Cem%3EDeva%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20however%2C%20opens%20differently%2C%20with%20gritty%2C%20almost%20non-fiction-like%20imagery%20of%20Mumbai.%20It%20evokes%20the%20way%20%3Cem%3ESatya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1998)%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eintroduced%20the%20city%2C%20or%20like%20the%20restless%20frames%20of%20%3Cem%3EDeewaar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1975).%20No%20wonder%2C%20then%2C%20that%20Dev%20often%20finds%20himself%20framed%20against%20graffiti%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan.%20No%20wonder%2C%20even%20more%2C%20that%20right%20after%20he%20loses%20his%20memory%2C%20%E2%80%98Main%20Hoon%20Don'%20plays.%20And%20no%20wonder%2C%20most%20of%20all%2C%20that%20just%20like%20%3Cem%3EDon%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeva%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20too%2C%20presents%20two%20different%20versions%20of%20its%20protagonist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Meta%20Moment%20For%20Shahid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeva%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoves%20away%20from%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20stepping%20into%20an%20existential%20terrain%20that%2C%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20feels%20genuinely%20compelling.%20It%20gestures%20toward%20a%20critique%20of%20unchecked%20brutality%2C%20the%20kind%20so%20often%20wielded%20by%20alpha-male%20officers%20like%20Dev.%20There's%20something%20intriguing%2C%20too%2C%20in%20watching%20Kapoor's%20character%20struggle%20to%20reconcile%20with%20his%20past%20self%2C%20unable%20to%20fathom%20the%20aggression%20he%20once%20peddled%20so%20frequently.%20It's%20almost%20like%20a%20meta%20moment%2C%20an%20unconscious%20attempt%20to%20course-correct%20the%20hypermasculinity%20he%20so%20proudly%20championed%20in%20%3Cem%3EKabir%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bachchan%20hangover%20has%20been%20evident%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%E2%80%94so%20much%20so%20that%20had%20we%20traced%20it%20more%20closely%2C%20the%20final%20revelation%20would%20have%20felt%20inevitable.%20It%20was%20always%20about%20working-class%20rage%3A%20an%20absent%20father%2C%20a%20boy%20who%20grew%20up%20fighting%20the%20world%20for%20his%20next%20meal.%20For%20him%2C%20ideals%20like%20honesty%20and%20duty%20hold%20no%20meaning.%20They%20are%20the%20very%20things%20that%20stole%20his%20childhood%2C%20his%20family%2C%20his%20faith%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBachchan%20As%20Bait%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20this%20ode%20to%20Bachchan%20feels%20like%20Andrrews's%20hat-tip%20to%20a%20star%20who%20shaped%20him%2C%20it%20also%20reflects%20a%20pattern%20within%20Bollywood%3A%20one%20where%20heroes%20are%20built%20to%20tower%20over%20stories%2C%20where%20mass%20appeal%20drowns%20out%20psychological%20nuance.%20This%20shift%20isn't%20incidental%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20cinematic%20drift%2C%20where%20introspection%20is%20traded%20for%20spectacle%2C%20and%20complexity%20gives%20way%20to%20flamboyant%20hero%20worship.%20Where%20%3Cem%3EMumbai%20Police%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20an%20intimate%20character%20study%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeva%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20the%20outset%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20its%20protagonist%2C%20with%20all%20his%20flaws.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20Andrrews%20forgets%20that%20Bachchan%2C%20too%2C%20was%20a%20messiah%2C%20not%20for%20himself%20but%20for%20those%20who%20had%20none.%20His%20rage%20was%20not%20indulgent%20but%20righteous%2C%20not%20fuelled%20by%20vengeance%20but%20by%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alteration%2C%20then%2C%20holds%20moments%20of%20intrigue.%20But%20it%20never%20quite%20knows%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20legacy%20it%20seeks%20to%20honour.%20And%20in%20that%2C%20it%20becomes%20just%20another%20Bollywood%20cop-actioner%2C%20using%20Bachchan%20as%20bait%20but%20never%20embodying%20his%20rebellion.%20A%20film%20that%2C%20like%20much%20of%20contemporary%20Bollywood%2C%20chooses%20comfort%20over%20courage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anas%20Arif%20is%20a%20film%20writer%20and%20a%20media%20graduate%20from%20AJKMCRC%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738744740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fphauo4co_deva_625x300_05_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%