%20working%20pattern%20of%20young%20ones%20and%20they%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20user.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20being%20a%20millennial%20boss%20in%20India%20means%20your%20boomer%20boss%20wants%20you%20to%20run%20the%20office%20like%20it's%20Dunder%20Mifflin%2C%20while%20your%20Gen%20Z%20team%20wants%20it%20to%20be%20Zomato%20Blinkit.%20One%20side%20wants%20attendance%20at%209%20AM%20sharp%2C%20the%20other%20side%20thinks%20'login'%20means%20sending%20a%20'Good%20Morning'%20GIF%20on%20WhatsApp.%20And%20here%20I%20am%2C%20stuck%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20wondering%20if%20I%20should%20wear%20a%20suit%20or%20just%20show%20up%20in%20sneakers%20and%20hope%20no%20one%20notices!%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738741080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F3abreo7o_boss-generic_625x300_05_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgurgaon-entrepreneur-shares-challenges-of-being-a-millennial-boss-you-often-end-up-7638844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayank%20Sharma%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20Gurugram-based%20Human%20Resources%20(HR)%20firm%2C%20recently%20took%20to%20LinkedIn%20to%20share%20his%20struggles%20of%20being%20a%20millennial%20boss.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgurgaon-entrepreneur-shares-challenges-of-being-a-millennial-boss-you-often-end-up-7638844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20to%20take%20on%20OpenAI%20with%20Deep%20Research%20AI%20agent%20on%20Gemini%20mobile%20app%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738740897000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgoogle-to-take-on-openai-with-deep-research-ai-agent-on-gemini-mobile-app-125020500627_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Available%20on%20the%20